Token.Abstract: Notifies the delegate that the presence channel subscribed successfully.

Parameter.Name: channel
Parameter.Abstract: The presence channel that was subscribed to.

Parameter.Name: members
Parameter.Abstract: The current members subscribed to the channel.

Token.Abstract: Notifies the delegate that a new member subscribed to the presence channel.

Parameter.Name: channel
Parameter.Abstract: The presence channel that was subscribed to.

Parameter.Name: memberID
Parameter.Abstract: The ID for the new member.

Parameter.Name: memberInfo
Parameter.Abstract: The custom user data for the new member.

Token.Abstract: Notifies the delegate that a member subscribed to the presence channel has unsubscribed.

Parameter.Name: channel
Parameter.Abstract: The presence channel that was subscribed to.

Parameter.Name: memberID
Parameter.Abstract: The ID of the member removed.

Parameter.Name: index
Parameter.Abstract: The internal index of the member (depends on the order joined/left or returned in the server member list)
